      "body" : "Some people recently discussed this on IRC and a possible solution would be to place a sample `bitcoin.conf` during the initial datadir creation. The sample `bitcoin.conf` could contain (#commented out) all relevant options with some explanations.\r\n\r\nIt could also be stored under a different filename (`bitcoin.sample.con`) (some people might say the bitcoin.conf should only be created/controlled by the package maintainers).",
